16
00:03:40,053 --> 00:03:43,545
To já vhodila zapálenou sirku do petroleje.

17
00:03:49,862 --> 00:03:54,340
Zabila jsem je.

18
00:03:55,969 --> 00:03:57,730
Spokojený?

19
